--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.1.0, 2010-03-18
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Branched from aewm++ (timestamped 28 December 2008)
    * Abstracted keybindings
    * Toggle windows (Alt-Tab)
    * Close active window (Alt-F4)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 version 0.2.0, 2010-03-19
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    * Improved swapping of workspace
    * Renamed desktop to workspace
    * Removed all menus
    * Windows are tagged a workspace (can belong to several workspaces)
    * A workspace with all windows
    * Shortcuts for accessing workspaces (Mod4+<num>)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------